TY  - JOUR
TI  - On the Bootstrap of the Maximum Score Estimator
AU  - Abrevaya, Jason
AU  - Huang, Jian
AB  - [This paper shows that the bootstrap does not consistently estimate the asymptotic distribution of the maximum score estimator. The theory developed also applies to other estimators within a cube-root convergence class. For some single-parameter estimators in this class, the results suggest a simple method for inference based upon the bootstrap.]
